OL,3,CGuernsey States' latest accounts show
OL,4,C#63 million net surplus
OL,6,FDeputy Heidi Soulsby, Treasury lead
OL,7,Ffor Guernsey's Policy & Resources
OL,8,FCommittee, says: "It demonstrates why
OL,9,Fthere is a need to take a strategic
OL,10,Fapproach to the delivery of health and
OL,11,Fcare, as well as the need to generate
OL,12,Fmore housing, both of which are top
OL,13,Fpriorities of the States.
OL,15,F"The improved performance is
OL,16,Fencouraging, especially compared with
OL,17,F2022, although we know that the
OL,18,Funderlying pressures, as a result of
OL,19,Four changing demographics have not
OL,20,Fgone away and will need to be
OL,21,Faddressed."
