OL,7,Fincome and expenditure - overall
OL,8,Fpublic sector costs went up by around
OL,9,F6.5%, partly due to higher wages and
OL,10,Fmore staff on the payroll, but these
OL,11,Ffactors also helped bring in #10
OL,12,Fmillion of extra tax due to higher
OL,13,Fbanking profits.
OL,15,FThe total net assets of the States are
OL,16,Fworth #3.8 billion.
